                                                <b>FOX One Perk for 3 Months:</b> Limited-time offer. Offer is available to (i) new Verizon Home Internet customers who activate/install any Fios, 5G Home or Verizon Home Internet Lite internet service and (ii) new and existing postpaid Verizon myPlan customers (excludes business and data-only plans) who activate a new Frontier Fiber plan and enroll in the Mobile + Home Discount. To receive a $15/mo perk credit for 3 months, you must enroll in FOX One perk within 60 days after activation/install. After the 3-month promo period, or if the account is moved to an ineligible service during the 3-month promo period, the perk credit ends and the perk auto-renews at $15/mo (or then-current monthly price) unless the perk is canceled or unregistered. If you have not completed account registration with FOX One within 90 days of perk enrollment, the perk will be removed from your account. You can cancel the perk anytime in My Verizon at verizon.com. Limit 1 offer per eligible Verizon account. Offer subject to change.
                                                </p>
