                                                <h1 class="cmp-accordion-header u-textCenter u-textxsCenter u-fontDisplay u-textLineHeightTight u-text--40 u-text--md48 u-text--lg64 u-marginBottom--48">
                                                  <span class="u-screenReaderOnly">
                                                    Have questions about Verizon’s Mobile and Home packages? We’ve got answers.
                                                  </span>
                                                  <span aria-hidden="true">
                                                    <span class="u-text--lg48">Have questions about Verizon’s
                                                      <br class="u-showForMediumUp" aria-hidden="true"> Mobile and Home packages?
                                                      <br class="u-showForMediumUp" aria-hidden="true">  We’ve got answers.</span>
                                                    </span>
                                                  </h1>
                                                  <div class="cmp-accordion-items u-colorPrimary">
                                                    <details>
                                                      <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                        <h6>
                                                          I'm a Frontier home internet customer and have Verizon for my cell phone plan. Can I get a discount?
                                                        </h6>
                                                      </summary>
                                                      <div>
                                                        <p>Yes, Verizon offers a mobile and home discount for eligible Frontier home internet plans* and Verizon postpaid mobile plans. Connecting your accounts via our enrollment hub, will allow you to be eligible for the Verizon Mobile + Home internet discount. Get $15 per month off your home internet bill when you have both a Frontier Fiber internet plan and Verizon mobile phone plan and if you have Frontier Fiber 2 Gig, Fiber 5 Gig or Fiber 7 Gig plan, or the maximum speed Frontier Fiber Internet plan available in your area, get a credit for up to $10 a month for one of our mobile perks**. To get started, visit our <a href="https://frontier.com/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p1||||||I'm a Frontier home internet customer and have Verizon for my cell phone plan. Can I get a discount?|Mobile+ Home enrollment hub&quot;}">Mobile+ Home enrollment hub</a>.</p>
                                                          <p>
                                                            <i>
                                                              <span class="support-footnote">*<b>Mobile + Home Discount</b>: $15/mo discount on any Frontier fiber internet plan of $20/mo or more after all current promotions and discounts are applied (excludes taxes, fees, surcharges and optional charges), when combined with any postpaid Verizon mobile phone plan (excludes employee, business and data-only plans). Enrollment req'd. Discount applied in 1-2 billing cycles.</span>
                                                              </i>
                                                            </p>
                                                            <p>
                                                              <i>
                                                                <span class="support-footnote">**<b>Perk On Us</b>: Availability of each perk is subject to specific terms, and age requirements. Requires one paid perk on eligible Verizon mobile phone line. Up to $10/month credit will be applied to your Verizon mobile bill as long as one paid perk remains active on mobile account. Perk credit canceled if paid perk removed or mobile line or home internet plan canceled. Perk promotional offers are not eligible for the perk discount. Credit applied in 1-2 billing cycles.</span>
                                                              </i>
                                                            </p>
                                                          </div>
                                                        </details>
                                                        <details>
                                                          <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                            <h6>
                                                              If I'm new to Verizon, can I get a discount by bundling mobile and home internet?
                                                            </h6>
                                                          </summary>
                                                          <div>
                                                            <p>Yes. To access these savings, you'll need to sign up for any postpaid <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/plans/unlimited/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p2||||||If I'm new to Verizon, can I get a discount by bundling mobile and home internet?|Verizon mobile phone&quot;}">Verizon mobile phone</a> plan (excluding business and data-only plans) and sign up for a home internet plan, like <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/home/internet/fios-fastest-internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p3||||||If I'm new to Verizon, can I get a discount by bundling mobile and home internet?|Fios Home Internet&quot;}">Fios Home Internet</a> or <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/home/internet/5g/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p4||||||If I'm new to Verizon, can I get a discount by bundling mobile and home internet?|5G Home Internet&quot;}">5G Home Internet</a>. Existing LTE Home Internet customers may qualify as well. Which plan you sign up for generally depends on what service is available where you live.</p>
                                                            </div>
                                                          </details>
                                                          <details>
                                                            <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                              <h6>
                                                                If I already have a Verizon Home Internet &amp; Mobile phone plan, how do I sign up for the Mobile + Home Discount?
                                                              </h6>
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div>
                                                              <p>The Mobile + Home Discount is automatically applied to your Verizon Home Internet bill once you have both a postpaid Verizon mobile phone plan and <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/home/internet/5g/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p5||||||If I already have a Verizon Home Internet &amp; Mobile phone plan, how do I sign up for the Mobile + Home Discount?|5G Home Internet&quot;}">5G Home Internet</a> or LTE Home Internet. For those who sign up for both mobile and <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/home/internet/fios-fastest-internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p6||||||If I already have a Verizon Home Internet &amp; Mobile phone plan, how do I sign up for the Mobile + Home Discount?|Fios Home Internet&quot;}">Fios Home Internet</a>, you'll have to actively enroll for the Mobile + Home Discount. If you don't sign up for the discount at checkout, you can sign up manually later through your Fios account. Visit the <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/digital/nsa/secure/ui/mhdiscount/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p7||||||If I already have a Verizon Home Internet &amp; Mobile phone plan, how do I sign up for the Mobile + Home Discount?|Savings &amp; Promos&quot;}">Savings &amp; Promos</a> center in My Verizon*. Follow the prompts to sync your mobile and home accounts and get the discount.</p>
                                                                <p>For existing home internet customers thinking about adding a mobile plan, you can <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/plans/free-trial/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p8||||||If I already have a Verizon Home Internet &amp; Mobile phone plan, how do I sign up for the Mobile + Home Discount?|try Verizon free for 30 days&quot;}">try Verizon free for 30 days</a>.</p>
                                                                <p>
                                                                <span class="support-footnote">*Don't have My Verizon yet? Find out <a href="https://m.vzw.com/m/cQDJL4" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p9||||||If I already have a Verizon Home Internet &amp; Mobile phone plan, how do I sign up for the Mobile + Home Discount?|how to register&quot;}">how to register</a>.</span>
                                                              </p>
                                                            </div>
                                                          </details>
                                                          <details>
                                                            <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                              <h6>
                                                                Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?
                                                              </h6>
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div>
                                                              <p>Yes, depending on your plan, you may be able to use the <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p10||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|Mobile + Home Discount&quot;}">Mobile + Home Discount</a> with other Verizon discounts. Some eligible discounts include <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/featured/first-responders/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p11||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|first responders&quot;}">first responders</a>, <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/military/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p12||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|military &amp; veterans&quot;}">military &amp; veterans</a>, <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/featured/nurses/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p13||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|nurses&quot;}">nurses</a>, <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/featured/teachers/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p14||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|teachers&quot;}">teachers</a> or <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/featured/students/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p15||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|students&quot;}">students</a>. <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/support/auto-pay-faqs/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p16||||||Can I bundle together phone and internet for an additional savings if I already have a different discount?|Auto Pay monthly discounts&quot;}">Auto Pay monthly discounts</a>, may be available when you sign up for Auto Pay and paper-free billing. Some exceptions apply.</p>
                                                              </div>
                                                            </details>
                                                            <details>
                                                              <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                                <h6>
                                                                What other deals does Verizon offer?
                                                              </h6>
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div>
                                                              <p>Verizon offers a multitude of deals on <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/deals/smartphones/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p17||||||What other deals does Verizon offer?|smartphones&quot;}">smartphones</a> from top brands like <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/smartphones/apple/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p18||||||What other deals does Verizon offer?|Apple&quot;}">Apple</a>, <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/smartphones/samsung/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p19||||||What other deals does Verizon offer?|Samsung&quot;}">Samsung</a>, and <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/smartphones/google/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p20||||||What other deals does Verizon offer?|Google&quot;}">Google</a>, as well as <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/deals/products/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p21||||||What other deals does Verizon offer?|accessories&quot;}">accessories</a>. For home internet customers, we also offer <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/deals/home-internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p22||||||What other deals does Verizon offer?|great deals on Fios and 5G Home Internet&quot;}">great deals on Fios and 5G Home Internet</a> service.</p>
                                                              </div>
                                                            </details>
                                                            <details>
                                                              <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                                <h6>
                                                                How long does Verizon's bundle discount on phone and internet last?
                                                              </h6>
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div>
                                                              <p>Your discount will remain active as long as you maintain your qualifying plans, and both accounts remain in good standing. If you cancel either your mobile service or home internet service, you will no longer receive the associated monthly discount.</p>
                                                              </div>
                                                            </details>
                                                            <details>
                                                              <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                                <h6>
                                                                What are the best internet and wireless plans to bundle together?
                                                              </h6>
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div>
                                                              <p>The best plans for you will depend on what you and your family needs and what options you qualify for. Learn more about our <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/plans/unlimited/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p23||||||What are the best internet and wireless plans to bundle together?|phone plans&quot;}">phone plans</a> and <a href="/discounts/phone-home-internet-bundle/home/internet/" data-track="{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;impression&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;l6|p24||||||What are the best internet and wireless plans to bundle together?|internet options&quot;}">internet options</a> today.</p>
                                                              </div>
                                                            </details>
                                                            <details>
                                                              <summary role="button" aria-expanded="false">
                                                                <h6>
                                                                Are there any discounts if I'm a Starry Home Internet and Verizon Mobile customer?
                                                              </h6>
                                                            </summary>
                                                            <div>
                                                              <p>There are currently no active promos for Starry and Verizon Mobile customers.</p>
                                                              </div>
                                                            </details>
